Package: tntpr
Type: Package
Title: Data Analysis Tools Customized for TNTP
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Sam Firke [aut, cre], Jake Russ [aut, cre], Alex Spurrier [ctb]
Maintainer: Jake Russ <jake.russ@tntp.org>
Description: An internal TNTP R package that includes functions and templates
    customized with TNTP branding. It is intended for this R package to be a
    one-stop shop for R tools by analysts and other data users at TNTP.
